attributionInfo.brokerName: eXp Realty of Greater Los Angeles

data.description: Nestled in the heart of Apple Valley and close to the San Bernardino National Forest, this terrific one level home is just waiting for you to make it your own!  2005 square feet of living space with 4 spacious bedrooms, family room and two full bathrooms, it's perfect for a growing family with plenty of space for entertaining family and friends!  Features include AC, a wet bar, pantry, vaulted ceilings, copper plumbing, double pane windows, fireplace in living room, skylights and solar panels.  With nearly half an acre of land, expansion options are limitless!  Parks and schools are conveniently located within walking distance as well as shops and eateries.  Don't miss this one!
